      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017871&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=12350&rangeEnd=12427",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c1132650813ab6d7bg011ce7?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=12350&rangeEnd=12427"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017871_3_6121-6154",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6121-6154",
      "markText": "“家”这个词只是用来指四面有墙环绕着的一个人可以在里面睡觉的地方。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017871&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6121&rangeEnd=6154",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c1132650813ab6d7bg011ce7?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6121&rangeEnd=6154"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017871_13_6211-6268",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "6211-6268",
      "markText": "事实是，一个人常常不是明明白白地有两条路可供选择，一条路好走，一条路难走。有时候他只是身不由己地走上这条或那条路。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017871&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6211&rangeEnd=6268",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c1132650813ab6d7bg011ce7?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6211&rangeEnd=6268"
    },
    {
